OL,3,CAston Villa victory parade in
OL,4,CBirmingham to celebrate Europa League
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FAn open-top bus victory parade will
OL,8,Ftake place through Birmingham city
OL,9,Fcentre in celebration of Aston Villa's
OL,10,FEuropa League final win in Istanbul.
OL,12,FThe club, which marked its first
OL,13,FEuropean trophy in 44 years, said it
OL,14,Fwanted to create a "unique experience
OL,15,Ffor fans and players alike" after
OL,16,Fbeating Freiburg 3-0 on Wednesday.
OL,26,@vD@TOUwD@[O]
