FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779555957
OL,3,CAston Villa victory parade in
OL,4,CBirmingham to celebrate Europa League
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FAston Villa said the parade, featuring
OL,8,Fthree buses, will begin on Branston
OL,9,FStreet in the Jewellery Quarter at
OL,10,F4.30pm on Thursday before covering a
OL,11,F4.5km route.
OL,13,FThe club said in a statement: "This
OL,14,Fwill be an opportunity for those who
OL,15,Fmissed out on being in Istanbul to be
OL,16,Fpart of the team's homecoming ` and we
OL,17,Fcannot wait to bring the trophy home
OL,18,Fto you."
OL,26,@uD@_OUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
