CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779555957
OL,3,CAston Villa victory parade in
OL,4,CBirmingham to celebrate Europa League
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FThe Prince of Wales, patron of the
OL,8,FFootball Association and a passionate
OL,9,FVilla supporter, erupted into cheers
OL,10,Fat the match in Istanbul and called it
OL,11,Fan "amazing night".
OL,13,FThe club said the players will have a
OL,14,Ffull training session on Friday,
OL,15,Fbefore travelling to Manchester on
OL,16,FSaturday before Sunday's Premier
OL,17,FLeague match against Manchester City.
